Ozil has since thanked the Arsenal fans for the support he has received and is looking forward to representing the club once again.

The German playmaker tweeted: 'Thanks for your support following my injury. I'll come back on the pitch soon as I can to help #AFC. Now and in the future #MiaSanArsenal.'

Ozil's club team-mate and fellow countryman Serge Gnabry has also provided Arsenal fans with an update on his fitness as he has revealed he is back in first team training after recovering from a knee injury.

